Enum TargetType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TargetType>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TargetType>

    public enum TargetType
extends java.lang.Enum<TargetType>
    This enumeration describes the different possible types of Discover targets.

      • WEB_SERVICES

        public static final TargetType WEB_SERVICES
        The web services target type is used for integrating custom data crawlers with the Discover server. It has a web service API, which can be used to develop applications which can feed data to the Discover server.

      • OTHER

        @Deprecated
public static final TargetType OTHER
        Deprecated. 
        This constant will not be used in the FlexResponse API. It was initially intended to be used for backwards compatibility but instead, when new types are added, they will be added as new enum constants.
